name: Pizza Hut | Porvorim, Goa

reviews.review_text:
Very pleasing experience, well mannered staff and excellent service.
The food served here was better in quality than any other pizza hut pan India.
Choco- volcano cake was never served this way anywhere else before.
Kudos to the team,
The store manager Mr. Yogesh is very kind and co-operative.
Thank you Mr. Yogesh
& Love you pizza hut.

Pros:
Atmosphere in and around the restaurant is superb
Cons:
but the quality of the pizza is not as good as it was few years back..
Reason: they are compromising the quality to make up with the lower price of the new pizza..

Suggestion:
I would definitely recommend local pizza outlets.
Support local Goan pizza outlets, they will never compromise quality and will always give extra toppingðŸ˜…

The pizzas were decent but not outstanding. The crust was a bit too soft and lacked crunch. However, other items we tried, although I can't recall their names, were tasty. The service was okay, but I found the prices to be on the higher side. Personally, I'd opt for Domino's over Pizza Hut.
